<view class="container"><view class="page-head"><text class="eyebrow">PASS IT ON</text><text class="title">我的发布</text><text class="subtitle">及时更新商品信息，让交易更顺利。</text></view><block wx:for="{{items}}" wx:key="_id"><view class="item-card"><image src="{{item.images[0] || ''}}" mode="aspectFill" class="item-img"/><view class="item-info"><text class="item-status">{{item.status}}</text><text class="item-title">{{item.title}}</text><text class="item-price">¥{{item.price}}</text></view><view class="actions"><button size="mini" class="edit-button" bindtap="editItem" data-id="{{item._id}}">编辑</button><button size="mini" class="sold-button" bindtap="markSold" data-id="{{item._id}}">已售</button><button size="mini" class="delist-button" bindtap="delist" data-id="{{item._id}}">下架</button></view></view></block><view wx:if="{{items.length === 0}}" class="empty"><view class="empty-mark">✦</view><text class="empty-title">还没有发布</text><text>一件用不到的好物，可能正被同学需要。</text></view></view>
